{"tid":618853,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"皮膚唔知搞乜嘢","createTime":"2018-04-06T06:46:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T06:02:24.000Z","uid":180802,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4a62d56d054a3e75658efafe8bf9a5bb17eed99e","tid":618853,"uid":180802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T06:46:21.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n由中二，三開始皮膚出咗啲班印<br />\n唔知係咩黎<br />\n唔係暗瘡喇又唔凹凹凸凸<br />\n尚算平滑<br />\n遠睇唔覺近睇就好覺<br />\n有時候瞓醒覺起身又唔見有<br />\n但係過咗幾個鐘之後就會浮現咗出嚟<br />\n一啲都唔痕但係好似好恐怖<br />\n想問下大家知唔知係咩嚟<br />\n使唔使去睇皮膚科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/06/144552_4a20fba28cf7ea7559f54627698c6bc8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F144552_4a20fba28cf7ea7559f54627698c6bc8.png&h=8ef1869f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c09d49d7becc041a43cfaef0dec902754899767","tid":618853,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T07:05:56.000Z","msg":"屍斑"},{"pid":"6d3c1946caec85c38a9e32fe751ff1896a9c941e","tid":618853,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T07:07:10.000Z","msg":"樣衰嘅DNA"},{"pid":"c42fe9c446097386f9df0342944f4c4efed9e60f","tid":618853,"uid":59664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T07:07:38.000Z","msg":"毒氣攻心，打少啲飛機做多啲運動啦"},{"pid":"305b7991658392281288d665e9370d5806b71469","tid":618853,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T07:22:32.000Z","msg":"有啲似阿源"},{"pid":"665da7ab54bd352c86e4e96859cc626bbbca0db4","tid":618853,"uid":67840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T13:30:34.000Z","msg":"雀班同黑班，好多人都有"},{"pid":"26d7810be58aa093d5b500a91a2b8d5220335844","tid":618853,"uid":180802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"665da7ab54bd352c86e4e96859cc626bbbca0db4","tid":618853,"uid":67840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":